snippet.title: I Made MrBeast's 100 Million Playbutton! (Custom)
snippet.description:
Use code DANIELKRAFFT60 to get 60% off your first Factor box at https://bit.ly/3WAPGzh

More Playbuttons: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSh10HLKI-DiC1e5AQBx8KuSUl_FcMLIe

Follow please
‚û§ Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/danielkkrafft/
‚û§ Twitter - https://twitter.com/danielkkrafft

Alright so in this video I built MrBeast's Custom 100 Million Playbutton that I designed several months ago. It didn't go anywhere near as planned, but I am really proud of how it looks in the end. I will probably deliver this playbutton just like I delivered MrBeast's 50 Million playbutton as long as he still wants it. I am planning on taking a break from these crazy IRL projects for a while, because they take a long time and I miss making videos. Anyways, at least I didn't have a mental breakdown this time around, hope you enjoy!

//about
My name's daniel and I design things. Usually I do 3d modeling in blender but I'm now a metal worker thanks to mr beast apparently??? Who knows what I'll design in the future. If you have any ideas please let me know

snippet.title: Minecraft NOOB to PRO in 100 DAYS
snippet.description:
What is up, I'm Chad Wild Clay. My dream is to go from Minecraft NOOB to PRO after 100 days in Minecraft. I'm stuck in my house recovering from spine surgery and I've missed hanging out with you Spy Ninjas so I figured a Minecraft challenge is the best way to have fun with you all. 

Today is my first day of learning how to play Minecraft and the goal is survival of my first night. I need to learn how to build a Minecraft house. Maybe I need to watch a YouTube minecraft house tutorial. Then I'll need to figure out how to put a bed in the house and sleep my first night. Hopefully, I can survive without running into any creepers, hackers, or zombies. 

If I become a true Minecraft Pro, maybe I can play with one of my favorite Minecraft YouTubers. Here are some of fun Minecraft gameplay:

PrestonPlayz - Minecraft Myths You Shouldn't Watch at Night...
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A2KhmZ3A0Ho

Cash - Cash Has A GOLD TOUCH In Minecraft!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VL9nTBnZ3Ho

Aphmau - Playing Minecraft as an UNHELPFUL Hamster!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IL-QzqGmIVE

Nico - Nico vs Cash MILLIONAIRE House Battle in Minecraft!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i99NV1sVzIY

GEVidsTV - NOOB vs HACKER: I Cheated In a BOXY BOO Build Challenge!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LP7-4gh_cWo
